{
  "stem": "9156.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to wait for-- for another train, and the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when you walk through the streets, you would see children with blown-up bellies with hunger, and, behind them, the stores were full of food.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was Spain.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I saw that with my own eyes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when we got into the place where they check your passport and all that stuff, there was a woman.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I carried a bag of bread from France.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she said, you don't need that anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I said, I guess not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Please.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So here's an official, you know, she's the one who checked you out, who wanted that bread.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In addition to that-- I mean that's Spain to me, at that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In addition to that, I remember that when we-- we wanted tickets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We needed tickets.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "No, we don't give you tickets to Portugal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But the man-- one of the men would traveled at the same time, he was apparently well-instructed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He pulled out some cigarettes and put them in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We got the tickets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Train tickets.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we sat in the train, behind-- I'll never forget that-- behind the train were children reaching out with their hands and begging for bread.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anything we had, we threw out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We said it will be there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, strange.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very strange.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Portugal immediately looked different from Spain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Very different.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not so many soldiers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not so much police.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When-- in Portugal, I was placed-- and this is the ISK did these things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was placed with a woman, a young woman about my age, I think.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were to wait for the boat, which would always take a few days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I did not know one word of Portuguese.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She didn't know any language that I spoke.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
